snippet.title: Duke Nukem 3D - The Thing [Outpost 31] reimagination [User Map]
snippet.description:
The outpost from John Carpenter's sci-fi horror movie "The Thing" remade in Duke Nukem 3D. Took 2 years to finish.

Download: http://www.moddb.com/members/forsete/addons/the-thing1
Download alternative version with monsters here: http://www.mediafire.com/file/7baub89zuba4c91/outpost31.zip/file
